NBA DRAFT 2016
June 23, 2016
Petr Cornelie
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   
 
THE MODERATOR: Could you just give us an opening statement about your game and what you bring to the Nuggets, please.   
PETR CORNELIE: I'm a power forward, stretch 4 man, so I can shoot the ball, I can rebound, bring some energy in the game, block, defense.   
 Q.  What are you most looking forward to about the NBA?  
PETR CORNELIE: I think it's the physical, yeah.  Everything is fast and tough, so yeah, it might be the physical.   
 Q.  Do you have a dream NBA matchup?  
PETR CORNELIE: I would say right now Porzingis, Kristaps Porzingis.   
  
  
  
  
  

END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT